The <strong><code>HTMLTextAreaElement</code></strong> interface provides special properties and methods for manipulating the layout and presentation of <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea" title="The HTML &lt;textarea&gt; element represents a multi-line plain-text editing control, useful when you want to allow users to enter a sizeable amount of free-form text, for example a comment on a review or feedback form."><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a> elements.